arts.ttl: Willem II down PEC Zwolle to go ninth
arts.sum: Willem II climbed to the top half of the Eredivisie after a slender 1-0 win over PEC Zwolle. Willem II headed into the game without a number of key attackers but they still managed to take the lead in the 11 minutes. Ringo Meerveld was sent deep by Patrick Joosten and he finished well.
